node.text:
Ever wondered WHY it's so hard to STOP doing something,  or why its so DIFFICULT to just SAY NO ..... 

Understand why and HOW and your more likely to be able break that damaging routine, kick that habit .... 

Over coming habits is half the battle when it comes to weight loss, when working with clients, I go deeper that just set plans to follow, I teach you HOW to follow them also. 

to find out more head to www.martynfordcoaching.com VERY limited spaces left.  #transformation #weightgain #fatloss #addiction

node.text:
It has become extremely popular and almost trendy to follow a Vegan or plant based diet...... HOWEVER is this the best choice for YOU and your goals? 

Obviously there are more major determining factors in this thought process for many, such as animal welfare, carbon footprint and so forth. HOWEVER if we are just looking from a health and performance perspective, there are a few factors to consider...

#vegan #plantbased #veganfood #nutrition #fitness #protein

node.title: Plant Based Protein Vs Animal Protein

node.text: It looked ALOT heavier when I was pressing it 😂😂😂😂😂 literally just DIED doing legs today, and loved EVERY minute of it. There is NO better feeling in the world, every day is one step closer to that goal.  20 years of training; and still I get butterflies 😂😂 #gym #love #legday

node.text: It's all in the eyes ... HOW badly do you want it.  I'm ready to get it all #focused

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Martyn Ford on July 19, 2021 tagging @emporiumgym, @warrenemporiumgym, @sforcewatches, and @wygnf_hugziiii. May be an image of 2 people, beard, biceps and indoor.

node.text:
Started the wk off strong ..... a trip back to where it all started 15 plus years ago.  They say Rome wasn't built in a day, and that's for sure.  The sun was out; the music was blasting and the new machines @emporiumgym were well oiled and ready to go ..... what an insane session. 

TOMORROW IS LEG DAY, and I'm already buzzing to get going.  So glad to feel this hunger once more, training makes me feel ALIVE .... nothing else in the world gives me this buzz, IF YOU KNOW, YOU KNOW .... genuinely mean it, when I say, I LIVE FOR THIS.  Also, big shout out to my bag carrier, he's getting mega SWOLE from it.  BIG up @wygnf_hugziiii 😂😂😂😂 #gym #backday

node.text: It's going to be a hot one ...... enjoying the sun and making the most of some rest.  Back on the grind tomorrow, the start of a new special .... make every Monday COUNT.  #mindset
